		<b>Comment By tomi, 2-24-06</b>
		<p>Jenny, I know exactly what you are talking about. My husband grew up in inner city Dublin, Ireland. The first time I went to meet my future in-laws they, knowing I was from "out-west", tried to make me feel comfortable by playing John Denver's Greatest Hits over and over and over...</p>
		
